casebody.data:
Friday, May 15, 1992

MOTION DOCKET

92-840. Farley v. Licking Cty. Court of Common Pleas, Domestic Relations Div.

In Prohibition. This cause originated in this court on the filing of a complaint for a writ of prohibition. Upon consideration of relator’s request for temporary restraining order,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that said request for temporary restraining order be, and the same is hereby, denied, effective May 13, 1992.
